profile: TJS Fireplace & Gas Services was founded in 1986 in Burlington. For over twenty-five years we have offered sales, service and installation of all gas fireplaces. We specialize in complete fireplace makeovers, wood to gas conversions, new gaslines and connections for appliances serving homeowners, renovation contractors and builders in the Burlington, Oakville, Milton and surrounding areas. References are always available. Call the company friends recommend at 905-630-5440 or email us at charles@tjsfireplaces.ca
